   Research Resources

   Loan Repayment Programs
     * NIH Extramural Loan Repayment Program for Pediatric Researchers -
       The NIH announces the availability of educational loan repayment
       under the NIH Extramural Pediatric Research Loan Repayment Program
       (PR-LRP).
     * NIH Extramural Loan Repayment Program Regarding Clinical
       Researchers - The NIH announces the availability of educational
       loan repayment under the NIH Extramural Loan Repayment Program for
       Clinical Researchers (LRP-CR).
     * The Contraception and Infertility Research Loan Repayment Program
       (CIR-LRP)
